name: Dawn5075
description:
Dear YT, I am minting this as an NFT just to confuse people back on earth in August, 2021. lol. I couldn't sleep of course, so I got up to watch the sunrise. Zahora will arrive later with the tools to fix the drive pod. Oh, and I almost got in a bar fight last night with some drunk guy trying to sell me his junky old XT-Landcruiser 4016 model for 15 tezos! Nobody even uses Tezos here! Shenanigans of 5075 I tell you. Miss you lots, Enoch

Recorded with: Nexus6 synthesizer, LABS, Elektron Model Samples *Special thanks to @wwworonin for the artwork.
